  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> Idle\n\n    Idle --> Viewed : A views B\n    Viewed --> Liked : A likes B\n    Viewed --> Idle : in 30 days\n    Liked --> Mutual : B likes A\n    Liked --> Idle : A cancels like",
