      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Idle是起始状态。那从Idle出来应该先到Viewed对吗？就是A浏览了B的资料页面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Viewed",
        "A views B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，触发条件是\"A views B\"。然后Viewed有两个去向：如果A点赞了，就进到Liked状态；如果没动静，30天后要自动回到Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Viewed",
        "Liked",
        "Idle",
        "A likes B",
        "in 30 days"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：Idle到Viewed，Viewed分支到Liked和Idle。Liked那边应该是双向喜欢的终点吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Viewed",
        "Liked",
        "Mutual"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Liked之后如果B也回赞A，就达成Mutual状态。但还要考虑A取消点赞的情况，这时候要退回Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Liked",
        "Mutual",
        "Idle",
        "B likes A",
        "A cancels like"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下取消点赞的流转：是从Liked直接回到Idle，不是回到Viewed对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Liked",
        "Idle",
        "A cancels like"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，取消就直接回Idle，相当于重置。另外起点要用[*]表示初始伪状态，图类型用stateDiagram-v2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Idle",
        "stateDiagram-v2"
      ],
